{"tid":2352075,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：同時簽入多位球員是技術性失誤","createTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T18:11:27.000Z","uid":343520,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac75f894fc608ed27509386a2d007aee1b020adc","tid":2352075,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"雲加說：「在我們看來，如果你購入了3名以上球員，那就是一種<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">技術性失誤</span></strong></span>，因為<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">你的陣容將因此失去平衡</span></span></strong>。我很清楚在英格蘭，大家都喜歡看到球隊購入強援，但<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">當你購入大量新援後，你的球隊就充滿很多變數，因為你無法預測他們的表現。</span></strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n「事實上，你應該去找到一個能讓球隊更加穩定的方法。當然，購買新球員有時候確實很有效，但對於球隊的穩定性來說，還是存在風險的，尤其是在技戰術的一致性上。我相信只要你能夠將注意力集中在自己身上，能在比賽中發揮出自己的實力，那你就能贏得比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pegJLt3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpegJLt3.jpg&h=e6ab8b55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fd2c5b3667dbacbf9c50d3aa862120fb879f5d8","tid":2352075,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:17.000Z","msg":"唔打機？"},{"pid":"ec0737a467d8ddd82ba7a264fcbcbf39e169fce5","tid":2352075,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4fd2c5b3667dbacbf9c50d3aa862120fb879f5d8","tid":2352075,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:17.000Z","msg":"唔打機？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"冇psplus"},{"pid":"7c8b7121986489ad586dfac8fc40c911ebc0f960","tid":2352075,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"仲有Mandy 未一字排開影相"},{"pid":"c22c39768d6bb1cd15c4b4db457e96e6c9fadd57","tid":2352075,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec0737a467d8ddd82ba7a264fcbcbf39e169fce5","tid":2352075,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4fd2c5b3667dbacbf9c50d3aa862120fb